go-to: election_algorithm
set-jump: post_election

@post_election
on-arrival: {!
// set congress proportion to votes
Q.shp_r = Q.shp_votes;
Q.anap_r = Q.anap_votes;
Q.tsp_r = Q.tsp_votes;
Q.dsp_r = Q.dsp_votes;
Q.dyp_r = Q.dyp_votes;
Q.mcp_r = Q.mcp_votes;
Q.refah_r = Q.refah_votes;
Q.other_r = Q.other_votes;

// The largest party can only be the NSDAP or the SPD.
Q.largest_party = 'SHP';
if (Q.refah_r >= Q.shp_r && Q.refah_r >= Q.tsp_r) {
    Q.largest_party = 'Refah';
}
if (Q.tsp_r >= Q.shp_r && Q.tsp_r >= Q.refah_r) {
    Q.largest_party = 'TSP';
}

// coalitions
Q.weimar_coalition = Q.shp_r + Q.dsp_r + Q.anap_r;
Q.grand_coalition = Q.shp_r + Q.dsp_r + Q.anap_r + Q.dyp_r;
Q.bourgeois_coalition = Q.dsp_r + Q.anap_r + Q.dyp_r + Q.other_r;
Q.center_right_coalition = Q.anap_r + Q.dsp_r + Q.dyp_r + Q.other_r + Q.mcp_r;
Q.right_coalition = Q.anap_r + Q.dyp_r + Q.other_r + Q.mcp_r;
Q.far_right_coalition = Q.mcp_r + Q.refah_r;
Q.left_coalition = Q.shp_r + Q.tsp_r;
// this is an absurd concept lol
Q.united_front_coalition = Q.shp_r + Q.tsp_r + Q.anap_r + Q.dsp_r;
Q.anti_democratic_coalition = Q.tsp_r + Q.refah_r;
// aka everyone except nazi, kpd, dnvp
Q.neo_weimar_coalition = Q.shp_r + Q.dsp_r + Q.anap_r + Q.dyp_r + Q.other_r;
!}

The electoral system is essentially proportional, with the proportion of Reichstag seats roughly equal to the proportion of votes.
 
**Election results:**

# 1991: 30, 1995: 25, 1999: 22
SHP: [+ shp_r +]

# 1991: 15, 1995: 15, 1999: 
ANAP: [+ anap_r +]

# 1991: 10, 1995: 13
TSP: [+ tsp_r +]

# 1991: 5, 1995: 4 (as DstP)
DSP: [+ dsp_r +]

# 1991: 9, 1995: 5
DYP: [+ dyp_r +]

# 1991: 14, 1995: 7
MÇP: [+ mcp_r +]

# 1991: 3, 1995: 18
Refah: [+ refah_r +]

# 1928: 9, 1930: 10
Other: [+ other_r +]

**Potential coalitions:**

ANA-SOL Coalition (SHP + ANAP + DSP): [+ weimar_coalition +]

Grand Coalition (SHP + ANAP + DSP + DYP): [+ grand_coalition +]

ANAYOL-SOL Coalition (ANAP + DSP + DYP + Others): [+ bourgeois_coalition +]

Milli ANAYOL Coalition (ANAP + DYP + Others + MCP): [+ right_coalition +]

